title: The Mill Valley gospel: Happy Day every day
text:
The Amazing Grace Gospel Show at Sweetwater The Amazing Grace Gospel Show at Sweetwater
By the time the Amazing Grace Gospel Show was over, the orderly crowd that had waited patiently in line to get into Sweetwater in Mill Valley was a lot less orderly, cheering and singing along with “Oh, Happy Day,” the great grand finale.
